hconcat.description: 2022 World Bank data, GDP per capita in current international $ and converted to purchasing power parity. Grey countries have missing data.
hconcat.name: view_1

subtitle: Ranking of countries per year.
Source: The Harvard Atlas of Economic Complexity (2022).

transform.calculate: datum.hs_eci_rank == 1 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'st' : datum.hs_eci_rank == 2 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'nd' : datum.hs_eci_rank == 3 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'rd' : (datum.hs_eci_rank % 100 in [11, 12, 13] ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'th' : datum.hs_eci_rank % 10 == 1 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'st' : datum.hs_eci_rank % 10 == 2 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'nd' : datum.hs_eci_rank % 10 == 3 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'rd' : datum.hs_eci_rank + 'th')

hconcat.description: 2022 World Bank data, GDP per capita in current international $ and converted to purchasing power parity.
hconcat.name: view_2

subtitle: Based on the Economic Complexity Index by year.
Source: The Harvard Atlas of Economic Complexity (2022).

transform.calculate: datum.hs_eci_rank == 1 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'st' : datum.hs_eci_rank == 2 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'nd' : datum.hs_eci_rank == 3 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'rd' : (datum.hs_eci_rank % 100 in [11, 12, 13] ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'th' : datum.hs_eci_rank % 10 == 1 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'st' : datum.hs_eci_rank % 10 == 2 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'nd' : datum.hs_eci_rank % 10 == 3 ? datum.hs_eci_rank + 'rd' : datum.hs_eci_rank + 'th')
